  <div id="left">
    <h1>TagTeam...</h1>
    <p>is an open-source RSS (and Atom) aggregrator with the power to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Aggregate anything that publishes RSS (Twitter, MediaWikis, blogs, Delicious, Zotero),</li>
